Chinese President Xi Jinping on Monday encouraged young people from both sides of the Taiwan Straits to work together to realize the Chinese Dream of national rejuvenation. Xi, also general secretary of the Communist Party of China (CPC) Central Committee, made the remark in his reply letter to 50 Taiwan youths participating the 20th Straits Youth Forum which was held on Monday and Tuesday in the coastal city of Xiamen in Fujian Province.